b4w_object_tags.title:
I'm happy to be curled into
a circle and put back in my
box for easy storage and
transportation

I have a flexible neck
for the best fit on your
piano

A soft pad under my chin
lets my head grip your piano
while you play

My nostrils have lights
which confirm when your
piano and smartphone
are connected

My USB ports
connect to your
piano or computer

Lights along my back
indicate keys on your
keyboard

My belly is shaped to
perfectly fit any piano
with full sized keys
